item.title: CVE-2023-0333|2024-08-02T05:10:55.163Z -- unknown -- templatesnext%20toolkit
item.description: The TemplatesNext ToolKit WordPress plugin before 3.2.9 does not validate some of its shortcode attributes before using them to generate an HTML tag, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
